<br>
The premise that the government shouldn't care if its citizens live or die isn't one likely supported by most people other than the most die-hard libertarians and certainly not one the government is going to adopt as policy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=happyalyssa>HAPPYALYSSA</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 112<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/8/03 4:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Evil?  Or just a good business practice?</span><hr size=1> /nod and <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/bvazaellecommunitycenter.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eloihim>eloihim</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Member</span><br>  Posts: 413<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(7/8/03 4:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fvazaellecommunitycenterfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=126.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Evil?  Or just a good business practice?</span><hr size=1> evil, not even going to argue this one. plain, simple evil.<br>
